QueryResultIF
public class SparqlTupleQueryResult
extends AbstractQueryResult

This class represents result of SPARQL tuple query.

It provides access to column names (result table header), sequential access to result values (result table rows) and single table cell values.

getObjectByItemURI

private TMObjectIF getObjectByItemURI(Value value)
Provides access to TMObjectIF objects in queried topic map. Value param is subject or item identifier.

Item identifier is URL pointing to topic map object stored/defined in the topic map file.
Format: file:/path/TMName.ltm#objectID
An Example: file:/ontopia/topicmaps/ItalianOpera.ltm#cause-of-death

Parameters:
value - URI supposed to identify topic map object
Returns:
TMObjectIF instance representing the referenced object otherwise null
